<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.6.4">
<l>vaimmi ṉummaṉat teṉṟu yāṉuraik kiṉṟa māyavaṉ cīrmaiyai</l>
<l>yemmaṉōr kaḷuraip pateṉṉatu niṟka nāṭoṟum vāṉavar</l>
<l>tammai yāḷu mavaṉu nāṉmuka ṉuñca ṭaimuṭi yaṇṇaluñ</l>
<l>cemmai yālavaṉ pāta paṅkayañ cintit tēttit tirivarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What do the likes of us have to say about the excellence of the trickster about whom I say:</l>
<l>“put your minds [on him]”? Let that be [as may be]. Every day the one who rules</l>
<l>the celestials, the four-faced one and the majesty with a crown of matted hair</l>
<l>wander praising, thinking of the feet lotuses of him because of [his] superiority.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
